HEADWORD: Artilize
<hw>Art"i*lize</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To make
resemble.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If I was a philosopher, says Montaigne, I would naturalize art
instead of <qex>artilizing</qex> nature.</q>
<rj><qau>Bolingbroke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Artillerist</ent>⟦br⟧
